VOTABLE.DESCRIPTION: User created table from data at the Extragalactic Distance Database: http://edd.ifa.hawaii.edu. VOTable is described at http://www.ivoa.net/Documents/latest/VOT.html
VOTABLE.INFO: SELECT pgc.PGC , kvcc.`VCC`,kvcc.`Name`,kvcc.`RA2000`,kvcc.`Dec2000`,kvcc.`RA1950`,kvcc.`Dec1950`,kvcc.`Mem`,kvcc.`Type`,kvcc.`Bt`,kvcc.`Vh`,kvcc.`Comment` from pgc LEFT JOIN kvcc on (pgc.PGC=kvcc.PGC) LEFT JOIN kleda on (pgc.PGC=kleda.PGC) WHERE (coalesce(kvcc.`VCC`,kvcc.`Name`,kvcc.`RA2000`,kvcc.`Dec2000`,kvcc.`RA1950`,kvcc.`Dec1950`,kvcc.`Mem`,kvcc.`Type`,kvcc.`Bt`,kvcc.`Vh`,kvcc.`Comment`) IS NOT NULL)

FIELD.name: PGC_ID
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: The Catalogue of Principal Galaxies (PGC) Number

FIELD.name: VCC
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Virgo Cluster Catalog number from catalog Virgo Cluster Catalog

FIELD.name: Name
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Common name from catalog Virgo Cluster Catalog

FIELD.name: RA2000
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Right Ascension (J2000) from catalog Virgo Cluster Catalog

FIELD.name: Dec2000
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Declination (J2000) from catalog Virgo Cluster Catalog

FIELD.name: RA1950
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Right Ascension (B1950) from catalog Virgo Cluster Catalog

FIELD.name: Dec1950
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Declination (B1950) from catalog Virgo Cluster Catalog

FIELD.name: Mem
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: M: considered a group member; B: considered background from catalog Virgo Cluster Catalog

FIELD.name: Type
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Morphological type from catalog Virgo Cluster Catalog

FIELD.name: Bt
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Blue magnitude from catalog Virgo Cluster Catalog

FIELD.name: Vh
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Heliocentric velocity from catalog Virgo Cluster Catalog

FIELD.name: Comment
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Comments from catalog Virgo Cluster Catalog
